377
00:16:57,970 --> 00:16:58,370
Mr. Song.

378
00:16:59,170 --> 00:16:59,810
I'll drink.

379
00:17:06,290 --> 00:17:07,650
Nice.

380
00:17:07,690 --> 00:17:08,050
Great.

381
00:17:08,570 --> 00:17:09,970
