399
00:17:47,250 --> 00:17:48,250
Fate.

400
00:17:48,610 --> 00:17:48,970
Right?

401
00:17:49,050 --> 00:17:49,370
Right.

402
00:17:49,890 --> 00:17:50,330
Good.

403
00:17:51,130 --> 00:17:53,210
Cheers to fate.

