433
00:18:55,290 --> 00:18:56,890
Of course, that's not the case.

434
00:18:56,930 --> 00:18:58,410
I have my full trust in him.

435
00:18:58,810 --> 00:19:00,090
It'd be a waste not to show off

436
00:19:00,130 --> 00:19:01,930
