476
00:20:28,170 --> 00:20:28,930
Not really.

477
00:20:28,930 --> 00:20:30,210
Observe your opponent.

478
00:20:30,730 --> 00:20:32,330
Maybe, at times,

479
00:20:32,650 --> 00:20:33,890
