00:20:59,490 --> 00:21:00,770
Everything about her.

492
00:21:00,810 --> 00:21:02,690
Xingchen is flawless.

493
00:21:03,010 --> 00:21:05,170
Sweet talker.

494
00:21:07,570 --> 00:21:08,010
Su.

