00:22:52,690 --> 00:22:53,090
Mr. Song.

534
00:22:53,810 --> 00:22:54,930
This is a card

535
00:22:55,650 --> 00:22:56,450
for my savings,

536
00:22:56,450 --> 00:22:58,530
