558
00:23:57,470 --> 00:23:58,710
We're a non-profit organization.

559
00:24:00,930 --> 00:24:01,650
Non-profit?

560
00:24:03,450 --> 00:24:04,170
That means

561
00:24:05,370 --> 00:24:06,170
