562
00:24:08,290 --> 00:24:09,610
Non-profit organization.

563
00:24:09,890 --> 00:24:11,090
Is the job

564
00:24:12,050 --> 00:24:13,330
unstable

565
00:24:13,970 --> 00:24:14,770
